-------------------------------------------------------------------
HISTORY OF PROGRAMMING LANGUAGES
hopl.org a site for timelining items about programming languages.
-------------------------------------------------------------------

It's constructed based on these principles:

> For a specific programming language <

- It should be at least used by a group of people.
- the date should be the formal release date.
- the description should be about the motivation these languages are based on.

> For a specific theorectical feature <

- The date should be the year when published.
- Better quote the paper/essay.

> For a specific practical feature <

- The date should be the one when a language implement it.
- Better relate to theorectical one.
